title: American Rifleman Magazine - January 1963, Reamer Making
description:
This is the complete January 1963 issue of American Rifleman magazine. PDF format.

I uploaded this issue because it has an excellent Keith Francis article on making chamber reamers.

Obviously there are other interesting things in these old magazines, in particular I like all the old advertisements.

If you would like to learn more about making reamers I highly recommend you get a copy of Guy Lautards Machinists Third Bedside Reader, also get a copy of the Machinery's Handbook
